Name: assign_worker_to_task
Description: Binary decision to assign a specific worker to a specific task.

Name: story_points
Description: The number of story points assigned to a user story.

Name: sprint_duration
Description: The duration of a sprint in days.

Name: feature_included_in_release
Description: Binary decision to include a feature in a release plan.

Name: task_start_date
Description: The start date for a task within a sprint.

Name: team_size
Description: The number of workers assigned to a team.

Name: worker_availability
Description: The percentage of time a worker is available for project work.

Name: blocker_resolution
Description: Binary decision indicating if a blocker is resolved.

Name: skill_level
Description: The proficiency level of a worker in a specific skill.

Name: sprint_goal_achieved
Description: Binary decision indicating if the sprint goal was achieved.
